Maina in court
ChannelsTV The Federal High Court, Abuja, on Tuesday, said that it would deliver its ruling on the bail application filed by the former Chairman of defunct Pension Reform Task Team, Abdulrasheed Maina, on November 7. Justice Okon Abang fixed the date after taking arguments from the defence and prosecution counsel, according to the News Agency of Nigeria.  



